    <note>"Mou(1) Lu [20748] There can be no doubt about lineage identification; Jiangsu jinshi zhi, 18.14a and WDY identify him as a Huzhou, Wucheng (modern Wuxing) county resident, who was from Sichuan. He was killed in 1370 at the hands of rebellious people (luanmin), and therefore could have been a relatively young man. Since he was not a son of Yinglong [20744] and does not share the generational name of Yinlong's sons, I am identifying him as a grandson of Yinglong. WDY, 1, 333."</note>
